ichest person in the world and the only one out of the 7.9 billion of us wi=
th a net worth over $200 billion. He recently flew to space on his own comp=
any&#8217;s spaceship. He&#8217;s done well, and everyone knows it.</p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em=
 0;">The incredible part of the Amazon story to me, though, is how and why =
